 ATTRIBUTE="library x11"
  HOMEPAGE="http://www.ping.de/sites/zagadka/guile-gtk"
       URL="http://www.ping.de/sites/zagadka/guile-gtk/download"
       REQ="gtk+ guile"
 FRESHMEAT="guile-gtk"
     SHORT="guile-gtk is glue code to make gtk+ accessible from guile"
cat << EOF
Guile-gtk is glue code to make the GTK+ (the Gimp Toolkit) accesible from
Guile so it provides a convenient interface for Scheme programmers to develop
visual applications.  It can optionally integrate with gnome via the
Gnome-guile module.
EOF
